data.description: EXCEPTIONAL!  ASTHONISHING!!  A RARE FIND....A TREASURE, INDEED!!!  The Welcome Foyer will introduce you to this Chosen Home that boasts 5-6 BRs, 4 Full BAs & 2 Half BAs!  And you will love the Open Living Space of the Den/Fam. Rm w/a Centered, Brick-Cased Gas Log FP w/an Eye-catching Built-in Corner TV Hutch, plus a Lg. Sunny Breakfast Dining area & the Awesome Fully Applianced Kitchen w/Spacious Granite Counter Tops & a Wondrous Mixture of Gratifying Cabinets.  Notice the Kitchen/Breakfast Dining Area's Woodburning FP & it's Open Wood Storage area...Well, that Wood Storage comes with a Bonus....be sure to ask about that!  :-)  The FDR has a Lovely Built-in Corner Hutch & Hidden Slide-out. There's a FLR ,as desired.  Expand your Extraordinary Living even more, in the INVITING Attraction of your quiet ''Backyard Viewing'' Planned SUNROOM!  It's a WOW, too!  And YES, there is a Lg. Utility/Mud Rm w/Dbl. Sinks, Agreeable Storage Cabinets, W & D hkup, Closets & a most convenient 1/2 Tiled Bath.  Another Awesome ''WOW'' is the Surprise Entertaining Theatre Area located in the Walkout Basement, complete with attached Lg. Wall-Screen, Movie Projection System (VCR not included) & Nice Built-in Shelves, Storage Cabs & more.  SO Many Stand-out Features:  Gorgeous HW Floors, Appealing Tile, Vinyl Floors., Accented Chair Rails, Beautiful Crown Moulding thru'out.  Ceiling Fans, Beautiful Chandelier Lighting. 1 BA has a Walk-in Tub/Shower w/Jets & notice, there is a Planned Capacious Jack & Jill Full BA, too.  Closets abound w/lots of extra shelving & the always needed extra built-in sized & designed drawers.  Up-stairs Cubbie Storage Window Seats.  *BRs upstairs freshly painted. Tankless HW Heater (2 mos.), Roof (approx. 12-15 yrs.)  Outlet for Tanning Bed in Basement TV area.  Lg. Entertaining Brick Patio.  Wired Outbldg & SO Much more!  Quiet, Peaceful Living at it's Very Best!   YOUR CAPTURED ''HOME SWEET HOME!''
